      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so im living in oslo and the sun is basically gone lol. i feel like my immune system is gonna tank this winter. i was reading some biohacking forums and people were saying you can take like 50,000 iu of vitamin d every day for a few weeks to really jumpstart your levels. is that safe to do just for a short bit to get ahead of the winter blues?",
