      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but i already had my blood work done a few months ago and they said i was pretty low. i just dont want to wait for another doctor's appointment for a simple thing like this. if i only do it for like 10 or 14 days, wouldn't that be fine? most of the people in those groups say it's basically just a loading dose to get you to a healthy baseline quickly.",
